library(corrplot)
## corrplot 0.92 loaded
library(stringr)
setwd("C:/Users/10713/Desktop/钢材性能预测")
a <- read.csv("a_use.CSV",stringsAsFactors = FALSE, header = TRUE, sep = ",")
b <- read.csv("b.CSV",stringsAsFactors = FALSE, header = TRUE, sep = ",")
c <- read.csv("c.CSV",stringsAsFactors = FALSE, header = TRUE, sep = ",")
e <- select(a, 4:6 | 9:34)
f <- select(b, 4:6 | 9:31)
g <- select(c, 4:6 | 9:31)
corrplot(cor(e),type="full",method="circle",tl.col="grey")

corrplot(cor(f),type="full",method="circle",tl.col="grey")

corrplot(cor(g),type="full",method="circle",tl.col="grey")

p <- ggplot(data = a,mapping = aes(x=粗轧压缩比, # 这里是x轴
                                   y=实验屈服值, # 这里是y轴
                                   colour = (str_sub(材料, start = 1L, end = 1L)))) #这里是钢的名字
p + geom_point(alpha = 0.5) + labs(title = "",subtitle = "钢种分组",
                                   x = "粗轧压缩比", # x轴名称
                                   y = "实验屈服值", # y轴名称
                                   color = "年份")
